ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次貨旗艦用次貨os 次貨cpu，完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大佬你send出黎條片用高通835喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己揾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食開殘廢餐？"},{"pid":"023e3b25cab5bb5649b5d844f1d04637fac5e6bf","tid":254100,"uid":76347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T17:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但重點係Android有個先天問題<br />\n當你用左某個時間，係明顯地慢左<br />\n呢個iPhone都有，但an機個情況會特別明顯好多</blockquote><br />\nnexus/pixel/pure google rom會唔會好d?</blockquote><br />\n會好d, 最貼近原生，少d background 野<br />\n但都有個個問題</blockquote><br />\n洗一次機就回復第一日感受啦<br />\n一兩年洗一次唔算好過份姐<br />\nbtw自己部m7唔係啲新app太大食唔夠揪都仲好順"},{"pid":"80f93e5dc8ff4485f46ace21a333880bc8d456fe","tid":254100,"uid":1953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"無知一問 <br />\nandriod 個wtsapp record 會唔會好似iphone 咁backup 去雲？"},{"pid":"a366790003f7491c1ce2249b0a3aa850d72cfe2f","tid":254100,"uid":36822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"條友S8更新左未<br />\n更新完ram man正常(Ray Ma, 2017)"},{"pid":"3852b8eb3bad2f667d876882ef95904d0f81bf86","tid":254100,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但重點係Android有個先天問題<br />\n當你用左某個時間，係明顯地慢左<br />\n呢個iPhone都有，但an機個情況會特別明顯好多</blockquote><br />\nnexus/pixel/pure google rom會唔會好d?</blockquote><br />\n會好d, 最貼近原生，少d background 野<br />\n但都有個個問題</blockquote><br />\n認真，啱啱出都咁既樣，三個月後ip8差距只會繼續放大。<br />\n早期<br />\n新an機旗艦效能最少屌打半年前iphone<br />\n到64bits世代<br />\n新an機旗艦降lv到效能啱啱過到半年前iphone<br />\n到6s<br />\n新an機旗艦連6s車尾燈都未見到。<br />\n而家<br />\n新an機旗艦連兩年前6s都追唔到。<br />\n<br />\nAn俠解釋就係用電話唔洗快。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬咁你唔洗買旗艦機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我對快慢定義就係一日你未可以秒速load到成個apps出嚟<br />\n你都要進步。<br />\n而an俠就用56k態度面對新一代旗艦差過兩年前機。<br />\n再嚴重少少，可以講埋s8差過6s等同代表s8差過se。<br />\n一部apple中價機。<br />\n如果有人覺得咁樣作為旗艦機夠，佢根本唔需要追旗艦。<br />\n突竟點解效能差左咁多？我睇法<br />\n1.Cpu廠不思進取<br />\n高通獨市同賣專利都賺到錢放軟手腳我明，三星自己都放軟就完全理解不能，自己當apple假想敵，以前都係靠效能起家，而家輸成咁無責任？<br />\n2.Android出事<br />\n聽落似google責任，但三星絕對有方法解決，好似跑分超頻打機降頻呢d反智行為。絕對可以由software改左佢。<br />\n3.apps出事<br />\n賴整app唔幫android仲易解決，你絕對出錢幫developer為你自己機種出改良版。無咁做邊個問題？<br />\n4.三星根本唔care<br />\n6gb android出足足一年<br />\n人地asus one plus講緊8gb ram.三星連砌番android top spec都唔願呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲同人講未來所有旗艦都行s8 spec<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ne plus 5將會屌打s8 note8，完。"},{"pid":"12c7811bc2c68e3ea7dc3eb5a412604ddc3380da","tid":254100,"uid":44,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T22:24:45.000Z","msg":"新牙膏廠Qualcomm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd37f6de7237e87eb1c3de1f38cc18f7c2ad8395","tid":254100,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:30:34.000Z","msg":"呢啲post究竟有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885697659eca1aed3ae08c94462a23a6304e3cc6","tid":254100,"uid":32887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲post究竟有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔明<br />\n用得android就係貪佢開放性夠高 可以做多好多ios做唔到既野<br />\n咁相對地付出小小代價我覺得無問題<br />\n<br />\nios係穩定係快 但唔岩我用咁解"},{"pid":"7d7174e9544d880c775f3f71f9aa987860724e32","tid":254100,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我已經中過an機伏<br />\nV10用用下可以boot loop嘅<br />\n永不錄用an<br />\n尤其係泡菜野，簡直係垃圾<br />\n轉用6s係用得唔慣<br />\n但舒服又run得順電又唔倒水<br />\n單係用家感覺好過an已經夠晒<br />\n小小缺憾冇問題</blockquote><br />\n泡菜廠新機都係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n識用an係sony"}]}